&lt;p&gt;You are welcome at St. Ann, Our Lady of Perpetual Help, and Mother of Sorrows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From time to time, the parish may take photos or video at public parish liturgies, events, and community gatherings to share parish life, preserve parish history, and encourage others in the Catholic faith.&lt;/p&gt;
